summary: The Bal\'Dorian Isle features a new quest and new worlds and items. We made this as a school project and decided to share it with te nexus. Your goal is to save a princess from an evil king, by gaining trust and support of the villagers and a mysterious person... Enjoy! Please leave a comment if you like it, so we can show our teacher. Thanks! :)
descriptionHtml:
The Bal\'Dorian Isle features a new quest and new worlds and items. We made this as a school project and decided to share it with te nexus. Your goal is to save a princess from an evil king, by gaining trust and support of the villagers and a mysterious person... Enjoy! Please leave a comment if you like it, so we can show our teacher. Thanks! :) Pictures added.
Check out our website (part of the project) for more information:
